    "description": "<p>Starting at 7th level, when you start your turn in an area of darkness or magical darkness, you gain a Darkness die, a d6. You can have only one Darkness die at a time. At any time, you can roll your Darkness die and apply the result to one of the following: your AC against one attack made by a creature you can see, an attack or damage roll you make with a weapon, or a Stealth skill check. You can apply your Darkness die even after&nbsp;making an attack roll&nbsp;or after the result of a creature&rsquo;s attack roll is declared.</p><p>At 15th level, your Darkness die increases to a d8.</p>",
